It doesn't happen overnight... but it DOES happen. Example, the european groups got here first... and now it's to the point where most european descended americans don't know thier racial background. Germans marrying the Irish, thier offspring marrying Italians and people of Polish descent... even Africans are starting to be accepted in that sense. The time will come for mexicans too... even quicker probably.<br>
<br>
Sharmila said:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
Ah, so this really IS about racism and not language. I kind of thought it was; your prejudiced remarks above make that clear. <br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
No, it isn't about race. I would be just as frustrated if they were speaking german or russian. I have never met a LEGAL immegrant (damn, what is with that word and me) who DIDN'T speak english. Maybe not perfectly, and almost certainly with varying degrees of an accent, but they spoke enough of it that we could carry on a conversation.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
By the way, I didn't &quot;advocate&quot; you losing your job -- I said that IF I were the employer and realized that you were in a position in which you spent 75 percent of your day doing stuff which isn't related to your actual job, I'd conclude I had a mismatch of job and employee, and transfer you. You appear to be in a position which calls for someone who is bilingual; you are not and so you are frustrated<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
&quot;transfer&quot; me where exactly? It's a retail clothing store... there is one job... sort of a combination stocker and cashier. I don't think my job SHOULD require me to speak a non native language in order to get my work done.<br>
<br>
Since there IS nowhere to transfer me to it leaves one option. Firing me and hiring someone who speaks a foreign language in thier own country.<br>
<br>
Carthos said:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
And perhaps if you wish to stop being treated as a spoiled brat, you'll stop acting like one. Answer me this: how do they give the impression of being second-class citizens? Please, explain that to me. Is it because they are different? I'd really love to hear your explanation. Oh, and God knows that someone who wasn't born in this country certainly doesn't deserve your job. They are clearly inferior<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
They give the impression of being second class citizens by NOT SPEAKING THE LANGUAGE OF THE COUNTRY IN WHICH THEY ARE CITIZENS.<br>
<br>
I don't think that is too complex to understand.<br>
<br>
And I don't care if someone who wasn't born in this country beats me out for a job... as long as I can say &quot;I lost this job because that person was better qualified&quot;. But I would be extremely pissed if someone who wasn't as qualified as I am for a given job was handed the job on a silver platter because of a damn language.<br>
<br>
Aishen said:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
In other words, get your @#%$ head out of your a$$. If it bothers you *that* much you would have enrolled in a foreign language class. Obviously, it doesn't bother you enough to that point, but enough so you come here and cry about the woes of your job picking up telephones.<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
  Why should I enroll in a foreign language class to hold a job in my native country?<br>
<br>
  As to your job... are you happy that those poor women are being counseled by someone with inferior skills? Does part of your help involve teaching them english so that they can be transferred to a counseler with the skills they need?<br>
<br>
  If I was raped and needed a counseler, I would be damn offended if I learned that my counceler wasn't the best I could of had, but instead was hired because she spoke a non-native language.<br>
<br>
as an aside, I DO applaud the work you are doing, and agree that yes, you need to have the ability to speak the language of your clients. Course... I still think we should catch all rapists, stretch thier equipment over a chopping block, and remove the offending parts... and since part of it's a mental defect, I suggest lobotomizing the sons of bitches too... but then theres the problem of proof... but thats another thread.<br>
<br>
My apologies if I come off as combative... it is not my intention. My intention is to get the frustration of practicaly being forced to learn a foriegn language just to survive in my native land. <p><center><A HREF="http://www.clanautumnwood.com" TARGET="_top">
<img src="http://www.clanautumnwood.com/graphics/kulani_sig.jpg"
